'''''Los Cabos Magazine''''' is a [[Mexico|Mexican]] lifestyle and tourism magazine with a special reference to [[Los Cabos]].<ref name="lbguide">{{cite web|title=Los Cabos Magazine|url=http://www.loscabosguide.com/magazine/|work=Los Cabos Guide|accessdate=19 June 2016}}</ref> The magazine was founded in 1993.<ref name="lbguide"/> From 2007 it is published on a quarterly basis.<ref name="lbguide"/> The magazine is published in English and provides information about Los Cabos targeting tourists as well as local residents.<ref>{{cite book|title=Fodor's Los Cabos: with Todos Santos, La Paz & Valle de Guadalupe|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ePRMBAAAQBAJ&pg=PT249|accessdate=19 June 2016|date=10 March 2015|publisher=Fodor's Travel Publications|isbn=978-0-8041-4361-5|page=249}}</ref><ref name="doh">{{cite book|author=Julie Doherty Meade|title=Moon Living Abroad in Mexico|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LJ_2CbVaNh4C&pg=PA458|accessdate=19 June 2016|date=8 May 2012|publisher=Avalon Travel Publishing|isbn=978-1-61238-286-9|page=458}}</ref> Its headquarters is in [[Cabo San Lucas]].<ref name="lbguide"/> It also has offices in [[San Diego]], United States.<ref name="lbguide"/>
